    "skill1": {
      "name": "Crimson Flower",
      "description": "Carmilla summons two Crimson Flowers that circle around her for 5s, dealing 100( +50% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) each time they hit an enemy and slowing them by 10% for 0.8s (the slow effect stacks up to 50%). The circling speed of the Crimson Flowers also increases with each hit. Carmilla recovers 75( +35% Total Magic Power) HP each time a Crimson Flower deals damage (only recovers 30% of that amount when hitting Minions).",
