      "strategicPurpose": "",
      "iconName": "Bloodbath",
      "tips": "With Bloodbath, Carmilla could control enemies with relatively high hit rate when roaming and therefore, assist her allies to slay targets.",
      "iconUrl": "/raw-assets/skill_icons/carmilla/bloodbath.png",
      "displayLabel": "Skill 2",
      "skillSlot": "skill2"
    },
    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Curse of Blood",
      "description": "Carmilla casts Curse of Blood on the target location, slowing enemies hit by 50%. After 0.8s, enemies still within the area will take 450( +130% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage), and will be immobilized for 1s, slowed by 15% and linked for 5s. When a linked enemy takes damage or becomes controlled, all the other linked targets take 50% of the damage and become controlled for 100% of the duration. Enemies can move away from one another to break the link.",
